1
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:37,020
=Royal Upstart 2=
(Based on "Zhenguan Foolish Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:37,325 --> 00:00:39,837
=Episode 27=

3
00:00:39,885 --> 00:00:42,600
(How Did This Brat Actually Do It?)

4
00:00:46,439 --> 00:00:47,040
Father-in-law.

5
00:00:49,799 --> 00:00:50,719
It's all settled?

6
00:00:50,919 --> 00:00:51,720
Yes.

7
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:56,119
Don't worry, Father-in-law.

8
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:57,359
It's no big deal.

9
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:59,519
I said I could handle it, and I did.

10
00:00:59,519 --> 00:01:01,590
They're even coming to
the engagement banquet on the 22nd.

11
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:03,920
Father-in-law,

12
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:05,320
is there anything else you need?

13
00:01:05,679 --> 00:01:06,600
If not,

14
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:09,760
I need to go pay a visit
to the lords at their mansions.

15
00:01:09,879 --> 00:01:11,600
Otherwise, they'll say I'm disrespectful.

16
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,280
You're only thinking
of visiting them now?

17
00:01:13,290 --> 00:01:14,660
What were you doing these past few days?

18
00:01:14,679 --> 00:01:17,479
Wasn't I busy preparing
the things to deal with the great clans?

19
00:01:17,479 --> 00:01:18,990
I just finished
getting them ready yesterday.

20
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:21,000
Don't ask me what I've prepared.

21
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,679
I can't say.

22
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:23,640
I gave the great clans my word.

23
00:01:24,119 --> 00:01:26,079
Otherwise, they'll really come after me.

24
00:01:28,079 --> 00:01:30,400
Father-in-law, if there's nothing else,
I'll head back.

25
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:33,640
I'll be very busy these next few days,
so I might not have time to visit you.

26
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:35,240
You must take good care of yourself.

27
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,000
Get out.

28
00:01:36,399 --> 00:01:37,200
Get lost.

29
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,620
For the next few days,

30
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,000
I don't want to see your face.

31
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,079
All right. Bye-bye.

32
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:46,359
(This brat... Come on.)

33
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:49,159
(He acts as if I
couldn't survive without him.)

34
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:50,330
Oh, right, Father-in-law.

35
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:51,680
Help me tell Mother-in-law

36
00:01:51,799 --> 00:01:53,439
that everything is fine now.

37
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,239
It's all settled.

38
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,519
Tell her not to worry.

39
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:57,599
Don't forget to tell her.

40
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,959
What method

41
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,040
did the fool actually use?

42
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,599
It must be that chest.

43
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,000
So exhausted?

44
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,439
Today,

45
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:29,000
I visited 12 Lords' mansions.

46
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:31,560
My voice is hoarse from all the talking.

47
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,200
Aunt,

48
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,200
what about you?

49
00:02:34,210 --> 00:02:35,200
How are the preparations?

50
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,799
Everything is fine on my end.

51
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,200
However,

52
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:40,560
there's something
I'd like to discuss with you.

53
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,359
You see,

54
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:46,640
over the years,
I've made some close female friends.

55
00:02:46,959 --> 00:02:49,640
I'd like to invite them
to the banquet as well.

56
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,520
But their social status

57
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,360
isn't as noble
as that of the high officials.

58
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,759
I'm afraid of embarrassing you.

59
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:57,879
Just invite them.

60
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:59,680
They're your friends, right?

61
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,360
Friends are equal, regardless of status.

62
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:03,400
Great.

63
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,159
Young Madam,

64
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:05,960
Young Master,

65
00:03:06,050 --> 00:03:07,400
the Clan Leader is here to visit.

66
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,800
What is he doing here?

67
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,850
It can't be anything good.

68
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,199
Show him in.

69
00:03:13,862 --> 00:03:15,700
(Qichi)

70
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:22,120
Why is it so warm in here?

71
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,039
It's this heater.

72
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,120
Hao made it.

73
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,120
It's exceptionally warm.

74
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,680
You brat.

75
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:31,800
To think you actually have such skills.

76
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,879
I was wondering why

77
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:35,560
Juxian Restaurant was so warm.

78
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:39,879
You came to see me,

79
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:41,319
so it must be about money, right?

80
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,599
You little brat.

81
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:49,039
Sometimes, you
aren't such a fool, after all.

82
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,120
Yes,

83
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,639
it is about money.

84
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:54,400
Regarding the money...

85
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,319
Wei Hao,

86
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,599
twenty thousand guan

87
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:02,280
is too much.

88
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,840
Even though the clan has it,

89
00:04:05,199 --> 00:04:07,879
we can't give it all to you.

90
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:09,120
If we give it to you,

91
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,639
and if anything

92
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,759
happens to the clan,

93
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,560
what will we do?

94
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,439
What 20,000 guan?

95
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:20,639
Hao, you're taking money
from the Clan Leader?

96
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,039
That won't do.

97
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:23,120
You can't break the rules.

98
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,360
I'm not breaking any rules.

99
00:04:25,919 --> 00:04:26,879
Really.

100
00:04:28,039 --> 00:04:29,639
What I mean

101
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,919
is that you should charge a bit less.

102
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,639
Don't be so ruthless

103
00:04:34,919 --> 00:04:36,879
toward your own clan.

104
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:39,680
Leave something for the clan.

105
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,240
How...

106
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,599
How much less?

107
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:48,439
How about 10,000 guan less?

108
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,840
Then, you tell me.

109
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:59,199
How much less?

110
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,040
I'm telling you,

111
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,160
one thousand guan at most.

112
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,560
Don't go too far.

113
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,879
Even though I blew up your gate,

114
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:06,639
think about it,
how much trouble did I save you?

115
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:09,199
And besides, didn't my aunt already
give you the money to fix it?

116
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:11,120
They have to pay me 20,000 guan,

117
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,550
and not a single wen can be missing.

118
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,560
Furthermore,

119
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:15,800
since I'm a member of the Wei clan,

120
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,190
I didn't even go all out this time.

121
00:05:17,330 --> 00:05:18,600
If I had really shown no mercy,

122
00:05:18,610 --> 00:05:20,950
would you still be in the mood
to talk about money here?

123
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:23,279
You'd better think about your own head.

124
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,720
Right.

125
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:26,560
Clan Leader,

126
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:29,319
what exactly is going on here?

127
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,920
It is like this.

128
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:33,519
It's due to some matters
within the clans.

129
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,439
I...

130
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:36,040
I can't go into the specifics

131
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,800
with you.

132
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:40,639
Because of these matters,

133
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,240
we must compensate Wei Hao

134
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,279
twenty thousand guan.

135
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,920
You are aware

136
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:53,120
that the clan does have this much money,

137
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:56,160
but we cannot give it all to Wei Hao.

138
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,839
Young Madam Lin,

139
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:59,920
please help me persuade him.

140
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,040
Aunt,

141
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,079
it has nothing to do with you.

142
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:06,360
Twenty thousand guan...

143
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,519
That much?

144
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,600
Think about it.

145
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:16,759
This money is the clan's reserve fund.

146
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:20,879
The clan has too many things
that need funding.

147
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:24,920
We need to provide
subsidies for those officials

148
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,920
and

149
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,639
scholars.

150
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,199
Also,

151
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,399
when there are

152
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:34,160
weddings or funerals in the clan,

153
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:37,480
the clan needs to provide the money.

154
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,519
Also,

155
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:43,319
if the clan suffers a huge misfortune,

156
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:46,519
the clan must also provide funds.

157
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:50,319
There are quite a few things
that need money.

158
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:52,759
Yes,

159
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,199
I know.

160
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,160
Tell you what,

161
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,240
I'll take the lead.

162
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:58,759
Then, let's reduce it by 2,000 guan.

163
00:06:58,839 --> 00:06:59,639
How about that?

164
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:02,519
Any more than that,
and it's out of my hands.

165
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,040
Well,

166
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,319
that's fine,

167
00:07:06,319 --> 00:07:07,079
but

168
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:10,240
could it be a bit less?

169
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,639
Come on, don't go too far.

170
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:15,079
Reducing it by 2,000 guan

171
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,800
is already showing you great respect.

172
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,600
Hao, how can you speak to
the Clan Leader like that?

173
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:23,279
How about this?

174
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:25,480
Let's make it another 1,000 guan less.

175
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,000
Clan Leader, don't say another word.

176
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:30,360
If you keep talking,
even the 3,000 reduction will be gone.

177
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,000
Fine,

178
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,199
three thousand less it is.

179
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,240
Wei Hao,

180
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:35,879
you

181
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:37,000
deserve this.

182
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,160
Clan Leader,

183
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,879
can you tell me now

184
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,399
what exactly is going on?

185
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:45,120
Yesterday's matter
has been settled, then?

186
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,240
What do you think?

187
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:49,639
I have even brought the money.

188
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,519
On the 22nd,

189
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,800
when you hold the engagement banquet,

190
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:57,160
the other clan leaders
and I will all attend.

191
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,800
This brat.

192
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,560
Looking at it from another perspective,

193
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:04,759
he has brought honor to our clan.

194
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,079
He is really a talent.

195
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,079
By the way,

196
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,399
Wei Hao,

197
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,879
since you are holding
an engagement banquet,

198
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,720
for

199
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,279
the younger generation of our clan

200
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,680
who are officials in the capital,

201
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:25,920
shouldn't you send them an invitation?

202
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,519
I don't have a list.

203
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,800
I have one here!

204
00:08:32,959 --> 00:08:33,800
How about this?

205
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:36,360
Tomorrow,

206
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:38,839
I'll have someone deliver it to you.

207
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,279
When the time comes,

208
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:43,720
you should also send someone
to deliver the invitations.

209
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,560
They really should be invited.

210
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,500
After all, he'll be
an official in court later.

211
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,240
Our own clan is more trustworthy.

212
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:50,600
Invite them if you must.

213
00:08:51,079 --> 00:08:51,879
Invite them all.

214
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,800
It's just a few more sets of chopsticks.

215
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,240
In that case,

216
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,560
I will head back first.

217
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,680
Hao, quick.

218
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,690
See the Clan Leader out.

219
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,759
Young Madam, I think there's
something fishy about this.

220
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,679
I've got it.

221
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:24,120
It must be because the Young Master
blew up the clan leaders' main gates,

222
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,990
and the compensation
is so high that he can't afford it,

223
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,840
but he can't tell you that directly.

224
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,279
So,

225
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,159
they conspired to put on this act.

226
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:36,240
The fool is really something.

227
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,960
Blowing up so many gates in one go...

228
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,279
No normal person
could ever do such a thing.

229
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,639
One main gate costs about 2,000 guan.

230
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,360
With so many gates,
how much would that be?

231
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,360
Wouldn't it wipe out
the entire clan fortune?

232
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,240
Young Master...

233
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,000
Xiu,

234
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:53,720
there is something

235
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,690
I've actually wanted
to tell you for a long time.

236
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,320
Go ahead, Young Madam.

237
00:09:58,679 --> 00:10:00,120
Even though Hao never knew

238
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,780
you were badmouthing him
behind his back,

239
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,960
I...

240
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:05,720
I really can't take it anymore.

241
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,679
Pack your things quickly

242
00:10:08,879 --> 00:10:09,960
and leave the Wei mansion.

243
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,559
Young Madam, please don't.

244
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:14,799
Now is the time
the Wei clan is thriving.

245
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:16,519
I can't leave right now.

246
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,399
So you know our clan is thriving, huh?

247
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,639
Then, who do you think

248
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,840
brought about all this glory?

249
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,039
It was the Young Master.

250
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,080
So, why do you always

251
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,240
twist the facts in front of me

252
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,950
and refuse to acknowledge
Hao's excellence?

253
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:30,759
I'm just not convinced.

254
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,840
What right do you
have to be unconvinced?

255
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,790
What made you forget
your place as a servant?

256
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,240
I'm just resentful.

257
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:38,480
Back then,
you could have taken me with you

258
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,919
to marry into
the Ningyuan Marquis's house.

259
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:41,919
But it was because of this fool

260
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,480
that your marriage was delayed,

261
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,519
and my whole life was ruined as well.

262
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,360
Ningyuan Marquis?

263
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:49,360
Did I even know him?

264
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,039
Young Madam,

265
00:10:54,170 --> 00:10:57,120
you don't even remember the eldest son
of the Ningyuan Marquis's residence?

266
00:10:58,639 --> 00:10:59,759
Why is it that you only

267
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:01,399
have eyes for Wei the Fool?

268
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,480
Is "Wei the Fool"
a name you're allowed to use?

269
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,399
Mister Wang!

270
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,440
Expel Xiu from the mansion.

271
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,890
She is never to enter
the Wei clan again.

272
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:15,320
Young Madam, don't.

273
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,120
Xiu, let's go.

274
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,440
I haven't even enjoyed
a good life with you yet.

275
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,240
Just go.

276
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,159
Young Madam is being merciful.

277
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,799
In any other household,
you would have been killed long ago.

278
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:26,039
Mister Wang, please plead for me.

279
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:27,320
Plead for you?

280
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:29,480
I've put up with you for long enough.

281
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,679
Plead for you?

282
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,519
Get out of here!

283
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:32,919
Still asking for mercy?

284
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:34,320
Go.

285
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:36,519
Don't drive me away.

286
00:11:37,887 --> 00:11:40,399
(Juxian Restaurant)

287
00:11:40,399 --> 00:11:42,320
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

288
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:43,159
Congratulations.

289
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:43,960
Careful now.

290
00:11:44,687 --> 00:11:46,048
(Juxian Restaurant)
Come, put it right here.

291
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:48,879
Please come inside.

292
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:49,960
Please come on in.

293
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,679
You brat,

294
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:55,480
not bad.

295
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,039
Mister Cheng,

296
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,919
you can drink your fill tonight.

297
00:11:58,919 --> 00:12:00,200
Don't you worry about that.

298
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:02,759
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

299
00:12:02,759 --> 00:12:03,360
Same to you.

300
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,120
Come, sit.

301
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,000
Sit down.

302
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:07,919
Hao,

303
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,080
they are...

304
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,200
The Ministers of Works,
War, and Revenue.

305
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,399
The Ministers?

306
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,279
Greetings, Your Highness.

307
00:12:16,279 --> 00:12:17,080
At ease.

308
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,080
Wei Hao,

309
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,080
you handled this matter brilliantly.

310
00:12:20,399 --> 00:12:21,080
I'm impressed.

311
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,080
Of course.

312
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,360
Brother-in-law,
you must drink well tonight.

313
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,279
Upstairs, please.

314
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,480
This way, please.

315
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:32,200
Young Master Wei.

316
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:32,840
Congratulations.

317
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,639
Congratulations, Young Master Wei.

318
00:12:33,639 --> 00:12:34,480
Thank you.

319
00:12:35,399 --> 00:12:36,519
Did you bring the things?

320
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:38,279
We brought everything.

321
00:12:38,279 --> 00:12:39,000
Aunt,

322
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,200
follow them

323
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,919
to the warehouse.

324
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,440
It's 20,000 guan for each clan.

325
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,399
How much?

326
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,799
Twenty thousand guan for each clan?

327
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:47,559
Go on now.

328
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:48,759
Alright.

329
00:12:49,279 --> 00:12:50,679
Gentlemen, please follow me inside.

330
00:12:50,679 --> 00:12:51,480
Alright.

331
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,919
I knew this brat had potential.

332
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,039
Just look at him.

333
00:13:00,159 --> 00:13:01,080
This brat

334
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,000
actually has such a capability

335
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:06,000
to get these heads of houses to attend
with so many gifts?

336
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,879
How do you think he did it?

337
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:10,120
I have no idea, either.

338
00:13:10,639 --> 00:13:11,480
In any case,

339
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,000
I couldn't have pulled it off.

340
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,759
Let's head upstairs.

341
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,000
Upstairs, please.

342
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,639
Alright.

343
00:13:16,639 --> 00:13:17,600
I bet

344
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,000
even His Majesty is curious.

345
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,120
Tonight,

346
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,320
we must get him drunk.

347
00:13:21,679 --> 00:13:22,600
Then, we'll ask him

348
00:13:22,879 --> 00:13:24,480
how he actually did it.

349
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,799
Good idea.

350
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:26,759
Cheng,

351
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,200
we're counting on you later.

352
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:32,519
Please.

353
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:35,720
Wei Hao.

354
00:13:36,159 --> 00:13:36,799
Wei Hao!

355
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:37,759
Coming.

356
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,559
Greetings, Father-in-law.

357
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:45,360
Greetings, Mother-in-law.

358
00:13:53,375 --> 00:13:56,205
♪Everyone says I'm a big silly fool♪

359
00:13:56,825 --> 00:14:00,225
♪When things happen,
I only know how to count on my fingers♪

360
00:14:00,995 --> 00:14:03,945
♪They shake their heads
and say I'm pitiful♪

361
00:14:04,285 --> 00:14:06,985
♪Sigh and walk away♪

362
00:14:08,585 --> 00:14:12,055
♪Little do they know,
I am sharp and bright♪

363
00:14:12,055 --> 00:14:14,285
♪With a heart like a mirror,
I understand the world's♪

364
00:14:14,285 --> 00:14:16,395
♪Colors and darkness♪

365
00:14:16,395 --> 00:14:18,415
♪But I keep my edge hidden♪

366
00:14:18,415 --> 00:14:22,775
♪The day I become famous
is just around the corner♪

367
00:14:24,215 --> 00:14:27,945
♪In the hotpot restaurant,
skewers boil in the broth♪

368
00:14:28,215 --> 00:14:31,815
♪People come and go,
with few worries or troubles♪

369
00:14:31,975 --> 00:14:34,055
♪The clacking of the abacus rings out♪

370
00:14:34,055 --> 00:14:38,845
♪See me differently.
Who dares to challenge me?♪

371
00:14:39,065 --> 00:14:40,685
♪The world mistakes me♪

372
00:14:40,685 --> 00:14:43,025
♪For an ignorant and stubborn fool♪

373
00:14:43,095 --> 00:14:44,285
♪As the storm approaches♪

374
00:14:44,285 --> 00:14:46,685
♪I just shrug and watch with a smile♪

375
00:14:46,895 --> 00:14:48,615
♪This foolish image is convenient♪

376
00:14:48,615 --> 00:14:50,595
♪I use it as a protective shield♪

377
00:14:50,765 --> 00:14:52,515
♪Navigating with ease, I attract♪

378
00:14:52,515 --> 00:14:54,615
♪A lucky star to accompany me♪

379
00:14:54,615 --> 00:14:56,085
♪In a peaceful golden age♪

380
00:14:56,085 --> 00:14:58,315
♪I hold my lady's hand
to watch the world♪

381
00:14:58,535 --> 00:14:59,735
♪Pouring youth and fireworks♪

382
00:14:59,735 --> 00:15:02,255
♪Into a precious glazed cup♪

383
00:15:02,385 --> 00:15:04,095
♪Having experienced life's changes♪

384
00:15:04,095 --> 00:15:05,375
♪And tasted its highs and lows♪

385
00:15:05,525 --> 00:15:06,945
♪My wish has finally come true♪

386
00:15:06,945 --> 00:15:07,985
♪To stay by your side♪

387
00:15:07,985 --> 00:15:09,905
♪In this fleeting world♪

388
00:15:10,075 --> 00:15:13,325
♪We are free and happy♪

389
00:15:17,325 --> 00:15:19,105
♪From a nobody♪

390
00:15:19,105 --> 00:15:21,005
♪To someone now famous♪

391
00:15:21,115 --> 00:15:22,545
♪Ordinary people laugh at me♪

392
00:15:22,545 --> 00:15:25,055
♪But I laugh at how
they cannot see through it all♪

393
00:15:25,155 --> 00:15:26,735
♪Let others plot and scheme♪

394
00:15:26,735 --> 00:15:28,805
♪I will keep my heart unchanged♪

395
00:15:29,015 --> 00:15:30,695
♪In this vast world♪

396
00:15:30,695 --> 00:15:32,695
♪I find my own leisurely freedom♪

397
00:15:32,845 --> 00:15:35,055
♪The world is bustling,
and things constantly change♪

398
00:15:35,055 --> 00:15:36,645
♪Everything ends eventually♪

399
00:15:36,735 --> 00:15:38,235
♪All that remains before my eyes♪

400
00:15:38,235 --> 00:15:40,635
♪Is this street wandering,
still tinged with pity♪

401
00:15:40,635 --> 00:15:42,345
♪No matter how time flies♪

402
00:15:42,345 --> 00:15:43,505
♪Even if the falling snow♪

403
00:15:43,505 --> 00:15:45,135
♪Dyes the hair at our temples white♪

404
00:15:45,135 --> 00:15:46,175
♪All I want now♪

405
00:15:46,175 --> 00:15:48,275
♪Is to pray for
my lady's peace and safety♪

406
00:15:48,275 --> 00:15:51,535
♪Year after year♪
